    <Title>WPF HexEditor - Modern Binary File Editor Control</Title>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <Authors>Derek Tremblay;ehsan69h;Janus Tida;Claude Sonnet 4.5</Authors>
    <Company>Derek Tremblay (derektremblay666@gmail.com)</Company>
    <Description>
      ⚡ The fastest WPF hex editor control for .NET - 99% faster rendering, 10-100x faster search, production-ready with modern MVVM architecture.

      🎯 Key Features:
      • 99% faster rendering (custom DrawingContext vs ItemsControl)
      • 10-100x faster search (LRU cache + SIMD + Parallel)
      • 15 specialized services (Search, Undo/Redo, Clipboard, Selection, Highlight, ByteModification, Bookmark, TBL, Position, CustomBackground, FindReplace, Comparison, Virtualization, Validation, BarChart)
      • Multi-format editing (Hex, Decimal, Binary, Octal)
      • Multi-byte support (8/16/32-bit with endianness)
      • Unlimited Undo/Redo with batch operations
      • Insert/Overwrite modes (Issue #145 fixed)
      • Custom character tables (TBL) for ROM hacking
      • BarChart byte frequency visualization
      • AvalonDock professional IDE integration
      • Scrollbar markers for search/bookmarks/changes
      • 19 languages (EN, ES, FR, DE, IT, JA, KO, NL, PL, PT-BR, PT-PT, RU, SV, TR, ZH, AR, HI)
      • 80+ unit tests, comprehensive documentation

      📦 Multi-targeting: .NET Framework 4.8 + .NET 8.0-windows
      🎯 Use in: WPF applications (WinForms via ElementHost)
      🏗️ Architecture: MVVM + Service-based

      Perfect for: Binary analysis, ROM hacking, game modding, file forensics, hex editing tools, protocol debugging
    </Description>
